data.description: Just reduced! Welcome home to the gated community of Esperanza de Buenavida estates! Upon entry you will note the newer plank style flooring, extremely high cathedral ceilings and grand staircase leading to the generously appointed landing upstairs. This light and airy, recently upgraded home boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 baths; one is downstairs. Your owner's suite boasts generous square footage, walk-in closet and roomy bath. Downstairs there are 2 distinct living areas and room for flex/dining, a nook and indoor laundry. In the chef-style open kitchen there are white cabinets and tasteful granite counters. Sit at the generous counter and look at fireplace AND your pool view! Outside you have dual zone AC and not 1, but 2 garages for a total of three spaces and a coveted gated courtyard in front. Easy freeway access and close to shopping, parks and walking trails, this one won't be on the market long. Hurry, Hurry!
